==反响==
得益于《刺客信条》系列对其心路历程的生动刻画和传奇生涯的精彩记述，艾吉奥这一角色在推出后即收获玩家与媒体一致赞誉。而作为唯一贯穿多部主系列作品的主角，他更被广泛视作整个系列的代表人物，总是在系列最受欢迎角色的投票中居于榜首。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/the-assassins-of-assassins-creed-ranked-from-worst-to-best/ |title=The assassins of Assassin's Creed, ranked from worst to best |newspaper=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |first=Andy |last=Kelly |date=2021-01-28 |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2022-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409052611/https://www.pcgamer.com/the-assassins-of-assassins-creed-ranked-from-worst-to-best/ |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://screenrant.com/assassins-creed-every-assassin-ranked-worst-best/15/?v=8 |title=Assassin's Creed: Every Assassin Ranked, Worst To Best |newspaper=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]] |first=Jason |last=Chamberlain |date=2017-06-22 |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2018-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009211558/https://screenrant.com/assassins-creed-every-assassin-ranked-worst-best/15/?v=8 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.lakebit.com/the-best-assassins-creed-characters/ |title=The 10 best Assassin's Creed characters |newspaper=Lakebit |first=Marcos |last=Tadani |date=2018-05-08 |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2021-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009232926/https://www.lakebit.com/the-best-assassins-creed-characters/ |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cbr.com/assassins-creed-5-best-protagonists-ranked/ |title=Assassin's Creed's 5 Best Protagonists, Ranked |website=[[漫画书资源网|CBR]] |first=Thomas |last=Mcnulty |date=2020-07-15 |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2022-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220221232319/https://www.cbr.com/assassins-creed-5-best-protagonists-ranked/ |url-status=live}}</ref>[[育碧|育碧]]也于2016年在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台单独为他推出过《艾吉奥合集》（The Ezio Collection），收录了除《刺客信条II：探索》外全部以艾吉奥为主角的游戏及影片。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2016/9/13/12903332/assassins-creed-ezio-collection-ps4-xbox-one-release-date|title=Assassin's Creed The Ezio Collection confirmed for November on PS4, Xbox One|first=Samit|last=Sarkar|website=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|date=2016-09-13|accessdate=2022-04-26|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405055039/https://www.polygon.com/2016/9/13/12903332/assassins-creed-ezio-collection-ps4-xbox-one-release-date|url-status=live}}</ref>

早在艾吉奥刚推出时，诸多评论家便给予好评。[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]]的编辑迈克尔·雷帕拉斯（Mikel Reparaz）认为，不同于沉着冷酷的前作主角阿泰尔，艾吉奥个性张扬且充满魅力，“更像是道德观模糊的超级英雄，而非无情杀手”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/assassins-creed-ii-11/ |title=Assassin's Creed 2 review |first=Mikel|last=Reparaz |work=[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]] |date=2016-12-01 |access-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731182013/https://www.gamesradar.com/assassins-creed-ii-11/|archive-date=2020-07-31|url-status=dead}}</ref>[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]的编辑威尔·塔特尔（Will Tuttle）则表示艾吉奥的最大特色就在于其成长性，从最初讨人厌的纨绔子弟，人生剧变使他担起责任，逐渐赢得玩家的同情与尊重。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ps3.gamespy.com/playstation-3/assassins-creed-2/1046764p1.html |title=The Consensus: Assassin's Creed II Review |last=Tuttle |first=Will |publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] |date=2009-11-17 |access-date=2022-04-27 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091121040638/http://ps3.gamespy.com/playstation-3/assassins-creed-2/1046764p1.html |archive-date=2009-11-21}}</ref>[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的编辑凯文·范奥德（Kevin VanOrd）毫不掩饰自己对艾吉奥的喜爱，称赞其角色完成度远高于阿泰尔。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/assassinscreed2/review.html |title= Assassin's Creed II Review |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |last=VanOrd |first=Kevin |date=2009-11-17 |access-date=2022-04-27| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100224100900/http://www.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/assassinscreed2/review.html| archive-date= 2010-02-24 | url-status= live}}</ref>《刺客信条：启示录》发布后，范奥德又表扬该作充分展现了艾吉奥身为导师的影响力，以及步入暮年的力不从心。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/assassins-creed-revelations-review/1900-6345201/|title=Assassin's Creed: Revelations Review|last=VanOrd|first=Kevin|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2011-11-14|access-date=2022-04-27|archive-date=2022-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427142544/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/assassins-creed-revelations-review/1900-6345201/|url-status=live}}</ref>《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》的编辑马特·米勒（Matt Miller）纵览《刺客信条II》到《启示录》，艾吉奥从一心复仇的少年成长为寻求智慧的男子，最终化身备受尊敬的导师，构成一道完整的人物弧光。<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.gameinformer.com/games/assassins_creed_revelations/b/ps3/archive/2011/11/14/assassin-39-s-creed-revelations-review-new-ideas-aren-39-t-always-good-ideas.aspx|title=Assassin's Creed Revelations Review|last=Miller|first=Matt|magazine=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|date=2011-11-14|access-date=2022-04-27|archive-date=2022-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427145100/https://www.gameinformer.com/games/assassins_creed_revelations/b/ps3/archive/2011/11/14/assassin-39-s-creed-revelations-review-new-ideas-aren-39-t-always-good-ideas.aspx|url-status=live}}</ref>《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》的编辑约翰·戴维森（John Davison）形容艾吉奥身处整个游戏的中心，如同《[[神秘海域系列|神秘海域]]》系列的主角{{le|内森·德雷克|Nathan Drake (Uncharted)}}，艾吉奥“迷人、风趣且富有自嘲精神”，能够更好地吸引玩家进入故事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/212960/assassins-creed-2/ |title=Assassin's Creed 2 Review |last=Davison |first=John |date=2009-11-17 |work=[[GamePro|GamePro]] |access-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100121133711/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/212960/assassins-creed-2/|archive-date=2010-01-21|url-status=dead}}</ref>

艾吉奥还是众多游戏角色评选榜单的常客。2009年艾吉奥刚推出，GameSpot就推选其为当年度“最佳新角色”。<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/special-achievement/index.html?page=6 |title=Best New Character - GameSpot's Best Games of 2009 |journal=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2009-12-21| access-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091222201830/http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/special-achievement/index.html?page=6|archive-date=2009-12-22|url-status=dead}}</ref>而在[[GameZone|GameZone]]全体女性编辑选出的“2009年度游戏之神”，即最具吸引力的男性角色中，艾吉奥位列第3。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gamezone.com/news/12_17_09_08_44AM.htm |title=The Top Five Gaming Gods of 2009 |year=2009 |first=Natalie |last=Romano |newspaper=[[GameZone|GameZone]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100201191351/http://www.gamezone.com/news/12_17_09_08_44AM.htm |archive-date=2010-02-01}}</ref>次年他又取得[[斯派克电子游戏大奖|斯派克电子游戏大奖]]“年度角色”的提名。<ref name="marysue">{{cite web |url=https://www.themarysue.com/2010-spike-video-game-awards-winners/ |title=The 2010 Spike Video Game Awards |work=The Mary Sue |last=Polo |first=Susana |date=2010-12-12 |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2018-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180704092836/https://www.themarysue.com/2010-spike-video-game-awards-winners/ |url-status=live}}</ref>随着时间推移，艾吉奥的影响力依然不减。《Game Informer》于2010年举办读者票选活动，艾吉奥荣登“十年来最受欢迎的30位游戏角色”第3名。<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/12/03/readers-top-30-characters-results-revealed.aspx |title=Readers' Top 30 Characters Results Revealed |first=Bryan |last=Vore |date=2010-12-03 |magazine=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2012-07-30 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120730191347/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/12/03/readers-top-30-characters-results-revealed.aspx |url-status=live}}</ref>2011年，[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]玩家版选出“史上50大电子游戏角色”，艾吉奥排在第35位。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2011/02/16/guinness-names-top-50-video-game-characters-of-all-time.aspx |title=Guinness Names Top 50 Video Game Characters Of All Time |newspaper=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |first=Jeff |last=Marchiafava |date=2011-02-16 |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65PklFpFu?url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2011/02/16/guinness-names-top-50-video-game-characters-of-all-time.aspx |url-status=live}}</ref>GamesRadar+曾于2012年和2013年举行两次评选，艾吉奥分别入选“7位最狠的新生代游戏角色”第2名及“50大新生代游戏角色”第4名，<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/top-7-most-badass-game-characters-generation/ |title=The Top 7... Most badass game characters of the generation |journal=[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]] |access-date=2022-04-27 |last=Cooper |first=Hollander |date=2012-09-28 |archive-date=2022-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427174003/https://www.gamesradar.com/top-7-most-badass-game-characters-generation/ |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-game-characters-generation/ |title=Best game characters of the generation |journal=[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]] |access-date=2022-04-27 |author=GamesRadar Staff |date=2013-10-11 |archive-date=2015-04-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Y7sHUm7I?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-game-characters-generation/ |url-status=live}}</ref>甚至在其近十年后的发布的“史上50大标志性游戏角色”及“史上最佳25位游戏英雄”榜单中，艾吉奥仍能分别位列第25与第8。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/best-game-characters/|title=The 50 most iconic video game characters of all time|first=Rachel|last=Weber|date=2021-11-08|access-date=2022-04-27|website=[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]]|archive-date=2022-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421180458/https://www.gamesradar.com/best-game-characters/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |first=Rachel |last=Weber |url=https://www.gamesradar.com/heroes-in-video-games/ |title=The best heroes in video games, ranked |journal=[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]] |date=2022-03-15 |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412134703/https://www.gamesradar.com/heroes-in-video-games/ |url-status=live}}</ref>无独有偶，《{{le|Complex (杂志)|Complex (magazine)|Complex}}》杂志也于同期发布过两份榜单，各将艾吉奥列为“10佳格斗游戏客串角色”第7位和“史上最狠的50大游戏角色”第37位。<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.complex.com/video-games/2012/03/the-10-best-fighting-game-cameos#5 |title=The 10 Best Fighting Game Cameos |date=2012-03-21 |last=Amirkhani |first=Justin |publisher={{le|Complex (杂志)|Complex (magazine)|Complex}} |access-date=2022-04-27 |journal= |archive-date=2012-12-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Cjt5F0sx?url=http://www.complex.com/video-games/2012/03/the-10-best-fighting-game-cameos#5 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.complex.com/video-games/2013/01/the-50-most-badass-video-game-characters-of-all-time |title=The 50 Most Badass Video Game Characters Of All Time |date=2013-02-01 |last=Avellan |first=Drea |journal={{le|Complex (杂志)|Complex (magazine)|Complex}} |access-date=2022-04-27 |archive-date=2014-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622100139/http://www.complex.com/video-games/2013/01/the-50-most-badass-video-game-characters-of-all-time/ |url-status=live}}</ref>此外他还位居{{le|UGO网络|UGO Networks}}评选的“最令人难忘的25位意大利游戏角色”第15。<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.ugo.com/games/top-25-italians-in-video-games?page=3 |title=The 25 Most Memorable Italians in Video Games |last=Meli |first=Melissa |date=2010-08-25 |journal={{le|UGO网络|UGO Networks|UGO Networks}} |access-date=2013-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029204548/http://www.ugo.com/games/top-25-italians-in-video-games?page=3 |archive-date=2013-10-29}}</ref>类似榜单排名也包括2016年《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》旗下网站Glixel发布的“21世纪50大标志性游戏角色”第7，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.glixel.com/news/lists/50-most-iconic-video-game-characters-of-the-21st-century-w449203/ezio-auditore-da-firenze-w449256|title=50 Most Iconic Video Game Characters of the 21st Century|author=Glixel Staff|date=2016-11-17|accessdate=2016-11-23|website=Glixel|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161123145238/http://www.glixel.com/news/lists/50-most-iconic-video-game-characters-of-the-21st-century-w449203/ezio-auditore-da-firenze-w449256|archive-date=2016-11-23|url-status=dead}}</ref>以及2021年《{{le|HobbyConsolas|HobbyConsolas}}》推出的“三十年来30大游戏英雄”第14。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hobbyconsolas.com/reportajes/30-mejores-heroes-ultimos-30-anos-816865|title=Los 30 mejores héroes de los últimos 30 años|first=Sonia|last=Herranz|work={{le|HobbyConsolas|HobbyConsolas}}|date=2021-03-01|access-date=2022-04-27|language=es|archive-date=2021-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210924043336/https://www.hobbyconsolas.com/reportajes/30-mejores-heroes-ultimos-30-anos-816865/|url-status=live}}</ref>

