13/the-best-playstation-beards-the-finest-facial-hair-gaming-has-to-offer/5/#gallery-top|archive-date=2012-11-29|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://mashable.com/article/most-datable-sexy-top-10-men-boyfriends-video-games/?europe=true#QRC0gYCJ_ZqY |title=The top 10 most datable men in video games, ranked |newspaper=[[Mashable|Mashable]] |first=Jess |last=Joho |date=2018-09-12 |access-date=2022-04-29 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515161854/https://mashable.com/article/most-datable-sexy-top-10-men-boyfriends-video-games/?europe=true#QRC0gYCJ_ZqY |url-status=live}}</ref>

